- Sun.

52
00:04:08,958 --> 00:04:10,749
Spun.

53
00:04:13,412 --> 00:04:16,888
Fun.

54
00:04:16,890 --> 00:04:19,967
Autumn.

55
00:04:20,085 --> 00:04:22,319
(water running)
ah, it smells so good!

56
