- You do this every month.

67
00:04:51,616 --> 00:04:54,042
- Yeah, and every month, I win.

68
00:04:56,455 --> 00:05:01,766
Come on, just let me contribute
until I find my own family.

69
00:05:01,768 --> 00:05:04,269
