87
00:05:46,430 --> 00:05:48,830
(joyfully exclaims)

88
00:05:48,891 --> 00:05:51,908
- Look at that.

89
00:05:51,935 --> 00:05:53,743
- Thanks, lori.
- Hey!

90
00:05:53,771 --> 00:05:56,563
