233
00:14:00,257 --> 00:14:02,131
Anytime.

234
00:14:04,911 --> 00:14:06,569
I'll call you.

235
00:14:06,596 --> 00:14:08,304
- Bye.

236
00:14:17,757 --> 00:14:19,082
(knocks)

237
00:14:19,109 --> 00:14:21,417
- Okay, it either went

238
