243
00:14:30,787 --> 00:14:32,912
- Okay, well, then,
give me the play by play.

244
00:14:33,031 --> 00:14:35,098
- Oh, he's...

245
00:14:35,125 --> 00:14:38,692
He's... So charming,

246
00:14:38,753 --> 00:14:40,753
And thoughtful,

247
00:14:40,872 --> 00:14:43,931
And, I mean,
he really listens,

248
00:14:43,933 --> 00:14:45,850
