01:08:54,430 --> 01:08:56,097
- Camping is gonna be
so much fun.

1139
01:08:56,099 --> 01:08:58,916
- Right? I love making s'mores.

1140
01:08:59,035 --> 01:09:02,937
I mean, a nutritious
vegetable sampler...

1141
01:09:02,939 --> 01:09:04,922
- Where are we going
camping again?

